※Do you want to see hints for a happy ending?

※If you fulfill the following conditions, you can go to the Araka Path
in the Happy End Horror Part: ① Collect all seven of Araka's relics
(they will be displayed in green text when obtained) ② Do not obtain
the key to the safe (do not be tempted by Carla).

※These conditions can be easily unlocked by using the Horror Path Skip
function.
Please defeat the final boss after fulfilling those conditions.
